{"tid":1953821,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"群體免疫，唔比派息，自己中L左就唔用華為報復，英國愈黎愈似一個Failed State。","createTime":"2020-04-01T11:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T06:55:36.000Z","uid":58287,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd63260ae114e09128d143d720df0bb537527af","tid":1953821,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n至於英國，首相莊翰生也患了病毒。據說首相在內閣會議大發雷霆，大罵中國瞞報害人，準備以踢走華為當做懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n這倒奇怪了。在邏輯上，是不是指即使若武漢肺炎病毒感染英國一半人口，只要他首相大人一直沒有事 ，就簽署華為加入英國的通訊網；首相遭殃，方將華為趕出門。<br />\n<br />\n但華為是電子高科技產品，武漢肺炎是生化物質，雖然同樣中國製造，卻屬於不同的學科。假如華為不威脅英國國家安全，即使武肺毒殺三千萬英國平民，華為也是安全的。若華為不安全，即使英國一宗確診也沒有，華為也一樣不安全。<br />\n<br />\n大西洋彼岸的川普看在眼裏，難怪心中暗笑。 <br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝"},{"pid":"2640cf91d3eed69ed3b8c067e78be606d8ad9f27","tid":1953821,"uid":58287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"講漏左哈里同條根。"},{"pid":"e038a01036c26def07fbfbae0c5850d4434d8e2d","tid":1953821,"uid":129924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:55:32.000Z","msg":"小心比人話你五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5ae986b8546cf4cada1c91d211b004426ce73b","tid":1953821,"uid":58287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e038a01036c26def07fbfbae0c5850d4434d8e2d","tid":1953821,"uid":129924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:55:32.000Z","msg":"小心比人話你五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"無人講，似乎大家都默默認同英國真係唔L掂。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be3effcb09617787a567b132e833c4e6ae47e57","tid":1953821,"uid":124983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj